{"tid":420781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃金周迪士尼搞乜？有無職員答下","createTime":"2017-10-01T16:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T18:16:46.000Z","uid":54424,"like":3,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"56bea3d3406590bfb2505df1ba9bc0eb6909a598","tid":420781,"uid":54424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:46:18.000Z","msg":"之前諗住支持下本地酒店，住左係迪士尼酒店，送左幾張樂園入場券就諗住玩埋佢。<br />\n今日入到去預左多粉腸，都算，入去行到明日世界，今日收1630大大個牌，乜鬼野事咁早收&hellip;只係心諗&hellip;玩左幾樣野想食個晏&hellip;唔好意思呢間餐廳又唔開果間又唔開，想食野又唔想食炸野啫，周圍都閂晒&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n然後四點無耐成個樂園既機動設施收得七七八八⋯⋯咩事呀⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n行行下去番新開個展覽館，成堆疑似內地人持票入場玩唔知乜蜘蛛俠試玩場，迪士尼唔係起好野就俾人玩殘先俾香港人玩牙？"},{"pid":"8d8c431471b34c4a9fa9b5a8f09ee1f344b1a7fd","tid":420781,"uid":11462,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:50:17.000Z","msg":"年年九月十月萬聖節期好多公司包場搞function staff outing<br />\n去之前要check左迪士尼個網<br />\n<br />\n利申:公司上星期先包完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c4d891d8840af3ea663352a7a7f05314bc4d0f","tid":420781,"uid":25641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3431497544eb32df37181e5b1a7b3059951ec3f","tid":420781,"uid":54424,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>年年九月十月萬聖節期好多公司包場搞function staff outing<br />\n去之前要check左迪士尼個網<br />\n<br />\n利申:公司上星期先包完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁佢前線員工應該知道包左乜野做乜野啦？但係我問職員啲餐廳有無開，唔知；我指住地圖，邊邊個遊樂設施仲有無得玩，唔知⋯唉&hellip;十問九妙答&hellip;我問得就係唔想摸門釘，結果妙答&hellip;唉！如果有團體租場，入口處就應該有話俾人知，又無指示，阿茂知迪士尼有唔入得既時候？"},{"pid":"7da7dcfc7fa9e16c275c4958c2eb2c4e08cd8264","tid":420781,"uid":18040,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:05:05.000Z","msg":"公司包場 <br />\n<br />\n尋日去完 <br />\n唔洗排隊就玩得真係好爽"},{"pid":"42fc0ee6d9117945f98a8f3733839e617ec83c54","tid":420781,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24755963a57886683a15928251d75a9793a658be","tid":420781,"uid":17619,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:15:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公司包場 <br />\n<br />\n尋日去完 <br />\n唔洗排隊就玩得真係好爽</blockquote><br />\nme2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後見到買飛入場D人冇得玩仲爽"},{"pid":"390ca24f30dd5105e15b36aa7e65bc2c791dd48a","tid":420781,"uid":16034,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>年年九月十月萬聖節期好多公司包場搞function staff outing<br />\n去之前要check左迪士尼個網<br />\n<br />\n利申:公司上星期先包完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁佢前線員工應該知道包左乜野做乜野啦？但係我問職員啲餐廳有無開，唔知；我指住地圖，邊邊個遊樂設施仲有無得玩，唔知⋯唉&hellip;十問九妙答&hellip;我問得就係唔想摸門釘，結果妙答&hellip;唉！如果有團體租場，入口處就應該有話俾人知，又無指示，阿茂知迪士尼有唔入得既時候？</blockquote><br />\n前線員工未必知架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢地剩通知你要去咩post"},{"pid":"6310b98ce43c1bbc9da25c805693a5477e58cf73","tid":420781,"uid":11462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>公司包場 <br />\n<br />\n尋日去完 <br />\n唔洗排隊就玩得真係好爽</blockquote><br />\nme2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後見到買飛入場D人冇得玩仲爽</blockquote><br />\n掛住塊牌 行入明日世界隊比啲大陸人睇仲爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc7c2d6c2abf3b77bc45bf7aa24315f0b21d4e2","tid":420781,"uid":11462,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>年年九月十月萬聖節期好多公司包場搞function staff outing<br />\n去之前要check左迪士尼個網<br />\n<br />\n利申:公司上星期先包完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁佢前線員工應該知道包左乜野做乜野啦？但係我問職員啲餐廳有無開，唔知；我指住地圖，邊邊個遊樂設施仲有無得玩，唔知⋯唉&hellip;十問九妙答&hellip;我問得就係唔想摸門釘，結果妙答&hellip;唉！如果有團體租場，入口處就應該有話俾人知，又無指示，阿茂知迪士尼有唔入得既時候？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/014726_837381542b565011743798b2d4ccccd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F014726_837381542b565011743798b2d4ccccd9.jpg&h=65c40ab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去迪士尼做足準備 <br />\n咁撚大個人上網都懶得上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1e98f18e8e7f0b55ead7fa9bf2a4b5c903a4e7","tid":420781,"uid":82640,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:50:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>年年九月十月萬聖節期好多公司包場搞function staff outing<br />\n去之前要check左迪士尼個網<br />\n<br />\n利申:公司上星期先包完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁佢前線員工應該知道包左乜野做乜野啦？但係我問職員啲餐廳有無開，唔知；我指住地圖，邊邊個遊樂設施仲有無得玩，唔知⋯唉&hellip;十問九妙答&hellip;我問得就係唔想摸門釘，結果妙答&hellip;唉！如果有團體租場，入口處就應該有話俾人知，又無指示，阿茂知迪士尼有唔入得既時候？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/014726_837381542b565011743798b2d4ccccd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F014726_837381542b565011743798b2d4ccccd9.jpg&h=65c40ab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去迪士尼做足準備 <br />\n咁撚大個人上網都懶得上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但啲員工都要同遊客一齊上網睇先知真係好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8036fd4a66c4592bdc82a81298a541eafe8b9da","tid":420781,"uid":11462,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:06:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>年年九月十月萬聖節期好多公司包場搞function staff outing<br />\n去之前要check左迪士尼個網<br />\n<br />\n利申:公司上星期先包完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁佢前線員工應該知道包左乜野做乜野啦？但係我問職員啲餐廳有無開，唔知；我指住地圖，邊邊個遊樂設施仲有無得玩，唔知⋯唉&hellip;十問九妙答&hellip;我問得就係唔想摸門釘，結果妙答&hellip;唉！如果有團體租場，入口處就應該有話俾人知，又無指示，阿茂知迪士尼有唔入得既時候？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/014726_837381542b565011743798b2d4ccccd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F014726_837381542b565011743798b2d4ccccd9.jpg&h=65c40ab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去迪士尼做足準備 <br />\n咁撚大個人上網都懶得上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但啲員工都要同遊客一齊上網睇先知真係好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一就迪士尼多Part Time做 好多都係識賣笑同派貼紙<br />\n其它Zone唔清楚都好正常 其他Zone可能明日世界比人包左都唔知<br />\n不過老實講 過安檢果時已經有塊牌寫四點半收明日世界<br />\n樓豬睇唔到怪得邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833bcf96b67cf29ade98cbdbfa6173a2c361e41d","tid":420781,"uid":3501,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:09:30.000Z","msg":"其實down迪士尼個apps睇咩資料都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n員工正路都會返工之前有briefing 講今日個park有咩活動、咩餐廳開咁樣<br />\n但唔係個個部門都會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmerchandise都可能會 但f&amp;b就難啲"},{"pid":"777616d792de1b22bb5f4fd4a2f7efe1ba89fa5b","tid":420781,"uid":10684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:12:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>年年九月十月萬聖節期好多公司包場搞function staff outing<br />\n去之前要check左迪士尼個網<br />\n<br />\n利申:公司上星期先包完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中銀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9b0efa9b49ddb286bb8348950b7211358879b4","tid":420781,"uid":81664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:46:20.000Z","msg":"今日我